Package com.hazelcast.partition

Interface ReplicaMigrationEvent

All Superinterfaces:
PartitionEvent
public interface ReplicaMigrationEvent
extends PartitionEvent
An event fired when a partition replica migration completes or fails.
See Also:
Partition, PartitionService, MigrationListener
